this_title: วุ่นนัก รักต้องประหยัด
introduction: Their grandma must have a headache, seeing the bills for expenses from twin grandsons 'Disco' and 'Hip-Hop' ordered the two to fly back to Thailand. Upon their return, they meet 'Money', a girl hired by her grandmother to take care of her 'Make Money' project, which is to do whatever it takes for the wrong twins. Together, these couples compete to work and earn money. Will it be able to complete this mission?
chinese_title: วุ่นนัก รักต้องประหยัด
